ASEAN Transport Ministers issued a ministerial declaration on ASEAN road safety Tuesday to enhance the road safety and reduce the traffic casualties in member countries.
With the road safety problem in the region has reached alarming proportion, Ministers determined to establish an ASEAN Multi- Section Road Safety Working Group to coordinate and oversee the implementation of the ASEAN Road Safety Strategy and Action Plan 2005-2010, adopted by the ministers Tuesday.
